title: New volcanic eruption threatens more delays for Bali travellers
text:
New volcanic eruption threatens more ... New volcanic eruption threatens more delays for Bali travellers Next Story Prev Story 1 hr ago Read more: The Age 
Virgin has delayed a number of flights from Australia to the Indonesian island on Wednesday morning so that conditions can be assessed, after an eruption at Mount Raung. Virgin flights out of Bali are currently on schedule but the airline has advised passengers not to travel to Denpasar Airport until they have had their rebooked flight confirmed.   The Age.
